Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:41.09,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}只是 被寫入大腦的虛象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.53,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}無限遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:49.03,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}不過是個 價值觀被改寫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:52.33,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}普通的平行世界
